snippet.title: My Lovely Empress - Coming August 21 to Steam, Switch, and Xbox
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam, Switch, and Xbox on August 21!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2052990?utm_source=homepage&utm_campaign=rda&utm_medium=yt

A tragic love story awaits you in My Lovely Empress. Play the role of an emperor who has had everything his whole life, and burn it all down for the one love he lost. Choose who gets to live another day in your glory, and who must die for your ambitions. There is no other way.
